# Sensitive config files
database.txt                 ✅ Ignores this specific file
scaffold.txt                 ✅ Ignores this specific file
*.secret                     ✅ Ignores all files with `.secret` extension
*.env                        ✅ Ignores all `.env` files
*.bak                        ✅ Ignores all `.bak` files (e.g., DB backups)
config/*.txt                 ✅ Ignores all `.txt` files inside `config/` folder only
appsettings.Development.json ✅ Ignores your dev-only config
secrets.json                ✅ Ignores user secrets
